init_text: Humans once wielded formidable magical power. But with over 7 billion of us on the planet now, Mana has spread far too thinly to have any effect. When hostile aliens reduce humanity to a mere fraction, the survivors discover an old power has begun to reawaken once again.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The ceremony was taking place in the centre of the city, in a large open area.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The energy would be focused into a single person, who would become the savior of humanity.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The Mana was flowing through the city, and the needle-like stones were glowing brightly.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The light seemed to be taking a form, and I could see a shape in the center of the light.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was a man, with a long, flowing cloak.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: This one was a woman, with long, flowing hair.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The light faded away, and the crowd began to murmur.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The High Priest raised his arms, and the crowd fell silent.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The aliens were tall, with long, gangly limbs.
